casebody.head_matter:
In re William M. WINDSOR, petitioner.
No. 16-6369 (R46-003).
Supreme Court of the United States
Dec. 20, 2016.
The petition for writ of mandamus and the motion for leave to proceed in forma pauperis were dismissed today pursuant to Rule 46.2 of the Rules of this Court.
